Package: frostr
Type: Package
Title: R Client to MET Norway's Frost API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Iman", "Ghayoornia", email = "ghayoornia.iman@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R client to MET Norway's Frost API <https://frost.met.no/index2.html>.
    frostr's primary function is to retrieve data from the Frost API as
    data frames, which can then be used, or combined with other datasets,
    for data analyses. The Frost API, and data, is made available by 
    The Norwegian Meteorological Institute (MET Norway). The data and products
    are distributed under the Norwegian License for Open Data 2.0 (NLOD) <https://data.norge.no/nlod/en/2.0>
    and Creative Commons 4.0 <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/>.
